content: I downloaded this app on the 2nd January. I haven't had a drink since. I am a heavy and regular drinker. I don't know when I last didnt drink for more than three days! Thank you so much for this brilliant, relaxing meditation that clearly works.

I drank everyday, honestly a bottle of wine after work and on weekends. Any excuse to have a drink I was. The hangovers and the moods I was in was affecting my family life. I have tried alcohol free days but they did not last. Found this app and gave it a go. A bit weird at start but kept persisting, every night I relax and really listen to Andrews words. I feel my body go into a deep state. I am on day 10 and don't have cravings or the need to drink. This is saving me and I am very thankful.
Listened once and stopped drinking. Great life hack! Thanks Andrew. Xant wait to see how else I can be reprogrammed!

Help! Pd for the app, embraced the initial 17 min meditation, but now all Im finding is links to his social media sights and ability to listen to the initial intro & meditation again. Am I missing something? Did I pay for a single meditation in hopes Ill buy into the other things offered (at addi cost) Confused!

Fantastic hypnotherapy app. I am now on day 27 sober and have no desire at all. This app helps me get off to sleep every evening and the healthy lifestyle suggestions have also clicked with me too. I am highly recommending this to anyone that wants to change their unhealthy habits.
I'm a psychotherapist, and I have 5 clients using this app, all with success. Thank you Andrew Johnson!

Amazed! I haven't gone a day of my adult life without drinking... I WAS an alcoholic... emphasis on WAS. Haven't drunk alcohol since week two of the app don't think about it dont want it. Absolutely thrilled!!!

Andrew Johnson is the best. I use this every night to go to sleep. It has also helped me with my not drinking . I am in recovery so the not drinking is just an added bonus. In my opinion this is my favorite Andrew Johnson app.

I can't believe how well this App works for me! I was a regular drinker, 7 days a week. After listening once, I've had virtually no desire for alcohol. ‚ò∫Ô∏è It's been 8 days with no problems passing up alcohol and I look forward to listening each day. I feel both relaxed and refreshed afterwards. And the money I'm saving is great!! I highly recommend this App. Thank you Andrew Johnson!

I want to cut down my drinking and I honestly though this meditation app would help but I don't have more than 30-40 minutes a day for it. Now you have 9 different meditations all lasting longer than the other. Meditation one is 31 minutes when meditation 9 is nearly 3 hours. I don't have 3 hours for a meditation. I truly believe this app would have been fabulous with 9 different 30 minutes meditations instead of hearing the same one over and over again. Not worth the $3...

Someone recommend this to me! It's a complete waste of time, could have got a pint in spoons instead ü§£ü§£.. No seriously though, unless I missed something? its just a 40 minute audio recording of some bloke telling you to relax and chill, and telling you your t total for life.. Jebus mate I still wanna have a beer and a bbq just not... ahhh well. it useless for me to be honest and a waste of money!
great meditation
Just don't
This actually works!

I am so greatful for this hypnotherapy. I am alcohol dependent for two decades. With this app I started step by step to work on 'clearing out' past memories, which kept giving me the idea alcohol is normal and a 'must have'. I am not quite off it yet, but for the first time I feel it made click - in my mind; I finally understand and I realise I can live without it. Thank you Andrew
I have been struggling with drinking for 10 years, but this app is helping me feel confident and happy about being a non drinker!
Nice relaxing app. Today is 15th day living sober.

It would be great but the music is so awful. I listened a few times and 
loved it but just can't do it anymore because of the music. Those tones 
haunt me!!
It's fantastic! Really works.
I'm a binge drinker and iv genuinely lost my desire to have a drink, after  listening for a just a few sessions.

I think it actually worked on me... I've broken a little drinking habit that I had. But.... Every so often the audio just stops for no reason... Needs to be fixed especially since I paid for it (rare for me to pay for an app) I don't know how to complain about this.
6 days sober and cigarette free. Not only has this  program helped me quit, it also helps me fall asleep fast
I am on day three and already feeling the benefits.  Needed to be in the right frame of mind myself to allow Andrew's voice and suggestions to sink in. Love it.üòòüòò

I didn't know what to expect from this app, and didn't really have the intention of completely stopping drinking, and yet nearly three months on and I haven't had a drop. Still have the same solid social life but feel more in control of my daily life. For the price it's well worth a shot! (No pun intended)
Great App very relaxing and finding useful. Thank u Andrew
Wonderful, so relaxing
Really helpful in breaking the habit of having a few drinks to fall asleep at night.
This app worked for me in 3 days, but I have been listening daily for a month.  I was a heavy drinker, but I have not and will not drink again. Thanks for freeing me from this bad habit!
The star rating is reflective of the ap, just that the Ap keeps coming up with an error message "stopped working" waste of money
Very relaxing and I see a very positive outcome for me..

I used this initially and it was crucial for me. Just listening to it sets you in a calm positive mood. The first few days/weeks/months of sobriety are tough, but so are You! And Andrew Drives that message home, you can be just as great or greater sober. THANKS!
Love this app! Andrew Johnson you are amazing! I noticed a difference in the first few days . Thanks heaps. This is saving me money and most of all my health
This app helped me enormously. I've tried so many techniques to stop drinking and have failed every time until using this.  Thanks Andrew!

Oh wow ! I didn't have any faith but this app truly worked. I have not had a drink since March 3rd 2015 and as Andrew suggests, I will not like drink again. Many thanks and blessings for improving my life, health and finances.

Story of my life, you saved my life Mr Andrew, you really have. I was addicted of alcohol and I was drinking every day and absolutely use to get drunk before I get to bed. My life is totally changed now. Being in a Muslim family it was very hard to keep my life on track as alcohol was causing many problems in family and other friends. This app really worked for me. Every time I think about alcohol I just remember Andrew's words. Very happy and hats off to you Mr Andrew. Highly recommended guys
Highly recommend
So successful this ap is for me...I no longer have any urge to drink alcohol and feel and look so much better. Still my hero Andrew x
Listened during my lunch break.  After work I stopped at my usual Tavern and ordered a drink.  Sat there staring at it f or 20 minutes and left. This after 20 years of daily,  heavy drinking.

I have had a drinking problem for five years... I drank every single day to the point of blacking out most days. I had finally had enough but didn't think I could do it. Trying to sleep was a scary enough thought alone as ive always had trouble sleeping.  After using this app for only a couple of days sleep became effortless and I had absolutely no cravings for alcohol. I don't know if I could have done it without this app. Sooo worth it!
A big thank you. To Mr Johnson. you have saved my life.x

Simple, positive, calming and effective. Id tried private hypnotherapy and many apps but none worked, until this. Thank you Andrew! Ive regained my life in just a week. Essential for anyone with a long term problem.

As a life long, heavy drinker, I knew I had to stop. My weight,health, job, finances (!!!) and relationship were all suffering. I didn't consider myself alcoholic, as I only drank after work.  I tried the App a few weeks before I planned to stop drinking one night and found myself in the pub the next day staring at my pint and wondering what I was doing! I  forced myself to drink it, and a few more after that!  The day before the day I planned to stop drinking,  my wife and I listened to the app again. The
If you really need help to stop drinking, DO NOT BUY THIS!!!!!!!!! ALL APPS GREAT EXCEPT THIS ONE!
